data.description:
OLD MILL BASIN 
Two Family Brick, Fully Attached house located in Old Mill Basin, Brooklyn, NY. 
Featuring a 2 Bedroom 1 Bath Over a 1 Bedroom 1 Bath. 1 Car Garage plus a Driveway. 
Top Floor features a private balcony overlooking the quiet neighborhood
Spacious backyard perfect for entertaining and gardening. 
Boiler and Hot Water tanks are less than two years old.
Property is close to Public Transportation, Shopping Centers, and Good Schools. 
Perfect for the Savvy Investor or First Time Buyer looking to make extra income. 
Call Anthony Garraud
